## 6.6 The Full Twinkle, Harmonized

Let's extend the harmonization to the full Twinkle melody (all four phrases). We'll add a bassline and chord changes:

```scheme
;; Full Twinkle Twinkle Little Star with bassline and chords
(define (twinkle-full-harmony)
  ;; Phrase 1: Twinkle twinkle little star (C major, I)
  (note/strike 'c5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'c5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'g5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'g5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'a5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'a5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'g5 'half 0.7)
  
  (note/strike 'c3 'whole 0.5)
  (note/strike 'e3 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'g3 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'c3 'whole 0.5)
  (note/strike 'e3 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'g3 'whole 0.4)
  
  ;; Phrase 2: How I wonder what you are (F major IV, then C major I)
  (note/strike 'f5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'f5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'e5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'e5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'd5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'd5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'c5 'half 0.7)
  
  (note/strike 'f3 'whole 0.5)
  (note/strike 'a3 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'c4 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'c3 'whole 0.5)
  (note/strike 'e3 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'g3 'whole 0.4)
  
  ;; Phrase 3: Up above the world so high (G major V, then C major I)
  (note/strike 'g5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'g5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'f5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'f5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'e5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'e5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'd5 'half 0.7)
  
  (note/strike 'g3 'whole 0.5)
  (note/strike 'b3 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'd4 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'c3 'whole 0.5)
  (note/strike 'e3 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'g3 'whole 0.4)
  
  ;; Phrase 4: Like a diamond in the sky (C major I, final cadence)
  (note/strike 'g5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'g5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'f5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'f5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'e5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'e5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'd5 'half 0.7)
  
  (note/strike 'g3 'whole 0.5)
  (note/strike 'b3 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'd4 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'g3 'whole 0.5)
  (note/strike 'b3 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'd4 'whole 0.4)
  
  ;; Final phrase: Twinkle twinkle little star (return to I, strong cadence)
  (note/strike 'c5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'c5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'g5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'g5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'a5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'a5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'g5 'half 0.7)
  
  (note/strike 'c3 'whole 0.5)
  (note/strike 'e3 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'g3 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'c3 'whole 0.5)
  (note/strike 'e3 'whole 0.4)
  (note/strike 'g3 'whole 0.4)
  
  ;; Final cadence phrase: How I wonder what you are (IV → V → I)
  (note/strike 'f5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'f5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'e5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'e5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'd5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'd5 'quarter 0.7)
  (note/strike 'c5 'half 0.7)
  
  (note/strike 'f3 'half 0.5)
  (note/strike 'a3 'half 0.4)
  (note/strike 'c4 'half 0.4)
  (note/strike 'g3 'half 0.5)
  (note/strike 'b3 'half 0.4)
  (note/strike 'd4 'half 0.4)
  (note/strike 'c3 'whole 0.6)
  (note/strike 'e3 'whole 0.5)
  (note/strike 'g3 'whole 0.5))

(twinkle-full-harmony)
```

