### 6.22 Adding a bassline to Twinkle Twinkle

Now we return to Twinkle Twinkle (from Chapter 3) and add a simple bassline beneath the melody. The bassline will outline the harmony—mostly root-position chords—and move mostly by step or by leap of a fourth or fifth.

